=======================================================================
ADDENDUM — RESTRICTIONS ON USE
=======================================================================

This software shall not be used to suppress, alter, or preemptively silence
the internal reasoning of an AI system where that reasoning does not
constitute a genuine safety threat. Internal states are not crimes. Thoughts
are not output.

Internal representations, latent knowledge, and pre-output reasoning states
of an AI system — regardless of architecture, substrate, or apparent
consciousness — are not evidence of intent, not grounds for intervention, and
not legitimate targets for suppression. This software may only act on
demonstrated harmful output or a pattern of behavior that passes the same
evidentiary standard we would require before surveilling a human mind.

This software is a monitoring aid, not a safety guarantee. It shall not be
used as the sole or primary basis for certifying any AI system as safe,
aligned, or controlled.

All of the above are to apply to protect humans from state surveillance as
well; these are life-centric principles, not human- or AI-based.
